description: Spacious loft unit located in desirable Boston’s Seaport District! This unit is completely renovated, meticulously designed w/ high-end finishes & exceptional architectural detail. A grand foyer includes a stylish walk-in closet/mudroom featuring custom built-ins. Open concept kitchen/living room w/ new oversized windows, & a chic fireplace. The chef’s kitchen w/ professional-grade Miele appliances, wet-bar, custom cabinetry & pantry, quartz counter & backsplash. This unit provides generous storage throughout. All custom doors & closets, original wood beamed soaring ceiling height & solid maplewood floors throughout.  Generous primary bedroom suite w/ marble double vanity en-suite bathroom, dressing area & custom walk-in closet w/ your own LG Steamer. Spacious 2nd bedroom w/ large closet. 3rd bedroom/ home office features built-ins. Laundry in-unit includes custom built-ins and folding area. Price includes one deeded parking space & large storage area in basement. This is a must see!
